                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City police-constable, No</hi>, 344.) I searched Betkins, and found this red silk handkerchief on him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Betkins's Defence.</hi> I bought the handkerchief a week before I was taken I took it off my neck.</p>
               <p>(Tilsley received a good character.)</p>
